Sign-up is open for the upcoming December Connectathon. The Connectathon will take place at the New Wave office located at 2270 Rolling Run Drive, Suite 400, Windsor Mill, MD 21244 on December 9 and 10. The sign up can be found here: http://bit.ly/DC-Connectathon-SignUp

There is no fee to attend the Connectathon and you do not have to be a member of CARIN to participate. Any developer who is a data holder or a consumer-facing app can join until we run out of space. If you have any questions, please let either myself or @Mark Roberts know.
